            <h3 class="heading-3">Transport</h3>

            <p>Stratton Court Barn is located just a few miles north of Bicester in Oxfordshire.</p>

            <p class="heading-4">Stratton Court Barn, Stratton Aubley, Bicester, OX27 9AJ</p>

            <p>There is free parking on-site and you're welcome to leave your car overnight so long as it's collected by 11AM the next day.</p>

            <p>If you plan to use a taxi service booking in advance is essential as our venue is located in the countryside. We recommend booking as far in advance as possible.</p>

            <p>Below are some recommended local taxi services:</p>

            <ul>
                <li>Alpha Cars Bicester: <a href="tel:01869252525">01869 252525</a></li>
                <li>Star Cars Bicester: <a href="tel:01869252526">01869 252526</a></li>
