            <h3 class="heading-3">Directions</h3>

            <p>Satnav Postcode: <strong>OX27 9AJ</strong></p>

            <p>From Junction 9, M40: Proceed through Bicester on A4421 towards Buckingham. Ignore the first two turnings towards Stratton Audley. Take the next right, signposted "Poundon" and "Godington". At the first crossroads, approximately 3/4 mile away, signposted "Chetwode" and "Gawcott", turn left. Pool Farm, Stratton Court Barn, is the first turning on your right.</p>

            {% render "components/atoms/call-to-action"
